Package: fintrackr
Type: Package
Title: Personal Finance Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Murali Karthik Ganji, Deeksha Reddy, Wesley Bowers
Maintainer: Murali Karthik Ganji <muralikarthik@arizona.edu>
Description: We have created an R package that aims to support personal
    finance analysis by providing tools for budgeting, investment growth,
    debt repayment projection, and financial data visualization. Users can
    summarize financial transactions, analyze trends over time, model
    investment growth with regular contributions, and simulate debt
    repayment schedules in a structured and user-friendly workflow.
